Inscribe and store your inscriptions in the world's fastest DRC20 wallet for Dogecoin!

Features

- Store and transfer your Doginals
- Inscribe (mint) on-the-fly without running a fullnode
- Store and transfer you DRC-20s

WIWW Wallet is a browser extension wallet that makes it safe & easy for you to store, send and receive dogecoin and doginals on dogecoin blockchain.
